Introduction

Jeon JiWoo is the main dancer, lead vocalist, rapper, and maknae of the CO-ED group KARD under DSP Entertainment. She represents the letter R which means the Color JokeR. She used to be an FNC trainee for 5 years and by the time she left and entered DSP Entertainment, it only took her 2 months before debuting on KARD.

Jiwoo debuted as a member of KARD on July 19, 2017, with the mini album "Hola Hola".

In 2020, she participated in Mnet's Hip Hop Reality Show, "Good Girl".
